    state: [
      { colId: 'price_code', pinned: 'left' },
      { colId: 'pic',        pinned: 'left' },
      { colId: 'desc',       pinned: 'left' },
    ],
    defaultState: { pinned: null }   // leave all others as the view says
  });
  ```
  Note: pass `applyOrder: false` so you don't reorder columns.

