When [row selection](ag-mcp://article/row-selection) is enabled, you can set the color of selected rows using the `selectedRowBackgroundColor` parameter. If your grid uses alternating row colours we recommend setting this to a semi-transparent colour so that the alternating row colours are visible below it.


