[Cell selections](ag-mcp://article/cell-selection) can be created by clicking and dragging on the grid. Multiple overlapping range selections can be made by holding `^ Ctrl` while creating a new range outside the existing range. Copying from a selection will briefly highlight the range of cells (`Ctrl + C`). There are several variables to control the selection and highlight style:


```
